title: Marriage Prospects for NFL Couples
itunes:title: Marriage Prospects for NFL Couples
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler bring you all the latest news around the NFL including the seahawks parting ways with Doug Baldwin (6:14) but adding Ziggy Ansah (10:32). In the fish tank we learn that Xavien Howard is expected to sign a 5-year, $76.5 million dollar extension (17:25). With Wess and Lakisha's wedding right around the corner, the heroes take a look at marriage prospects for NFL couples (30:15) and are joined by a special guest to close out the show. (49:51).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
